A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend an Act creating the Board of Commissioners of Douglas County, approved
2 February 15, 1952 (Ga. L. 1952, p. 2703), as amended, particularly by an Act approved
3 February 25, 1991 (Ga. L. 1991, p. 3501), so as to change provisions relating to filling of
4 vacancies on the board of commissioners; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting
5 laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 An Act creating the Board of Commissioners of Douglas County, approved February 15,
9 1952 (Ga. L. 1952, p. 2703), as amended, particularly by an Act approved February 25, 1991
10 (Ga. L. 1991, p. 3501), is amended by revising Section 6 as follows:
11 "SECTION 6.
12 Should a vacancy occur upon said board by resignation, removal, death, or otherwise,
13 except by recall as provided by state law, such vacancy shall be filled as follows:
14 (1) If the vacancy is a temporary vacancy:
